geo:Geography rdf:type owl:Class ;
              rdfs:subClassOf owl:Thing .


###  http://meteo_onto.org/meteo_geo/LocationType
geo:LocationType rdf:type owl:Class ;
                 rdfs:subClassOf geo:LocationType .


